      {
        "segmentId": "cat-line-01",
        "shotId": "open-stall",
        "text": "夜市刚亮灯，橘猫的炒粉摊开张了。",
        "outputPath": "generated/audio/cat-line-01.wav"
      },
      {
        "segmentId": "cat-line-02",
        "shotId": "heat-wok",
        "text": "客人说少辣，它先把铁锅烧到冒烟。",
        "outputPath": "generated/audio/cat-line-02.wav"
      },
      {
        "segmentId": "cat-line-03",
        "shotId": "add-noodles",
        "text": "米粉一落锅，它左爪倒粉，右爪稳住锅柄。",
        "outputPath": "generated/audio/cat-line-03.wav"
      },
      {
        "segmentId": "cat-line-04",
        "shotId": "stir-fry",
        "text": "豆芽鸡蛋一翻，香气飘过半条街。",
        "outputPath": "generated/audio/cat-line-04.wav"
      },
      {
        "segmentId": "cat-line-05",
        "shotId": "add-sauce",
        "text": "酱油沿锅边一淋，火苗呼地窜起来。",
        "outputPath": "generated/audio/cat-line-05.wav"
      },
      {
        "segmentId": "cat-line-06",
        "shotId": "toss-noodles",
        "text": "锅一颠，炒粉划道弧线，稳稳落回去。",
        "outputPath": "generated/audio/cat-line-06.wav"
      },
      {
        "segmentId": "cat-line-07",
        "shotId": "serve-customer",
        "text": "热腾腾的一盘递出去，客人的尾巴先摇了。",
        "outputPath": "generated/audio/cat-line-07.wav"
      }
